I could never handle that kind of attention. I just
feel like it would take over your whole life.

52:43.518 --> 52:56.915
Uh, all I do is I... try not to think about me. I
have people I care about. I focus on them.

52:58.793 --> 53:01.962
And the rest, uhm, it works out.

53:04.255 --> 53:10.240
You saved my life last night. I mean, I know
we re family but... you heard a thing on me.

53:11.564 --> 53:16.610
Makes me wonder, you know, if I'd be
brave enough to do the same thing.

53:18.622 --> 53:21.198
I really hope you never have to find that out.

53:24.847 --> 53:27.631
Oh, if you need me, you know where to find me.

53:28.121 --> 53:31.217
I'll be up in my cell, oh, I mean, my room.

53:55.634 --> 54:01.412
Our rooms are boarded up. That's the
view from my cell. It's really weird.

54:01.975 --> 54:05.446
I think Olivia would understand, ok? She'd
want me to be around other people.

54:06.322 --> 54:10.701
Holy shit. Even if I did just crash land on planet dork.

54:12.234 --> 54:15.257
Speaking of which, Trevor's here.
- Hey, Kirby.

54:15.257 --> 54:20.021
- What is he doing there? That is so not his scene.
- I have no idea, maybe he thought you would be here.

54:20.302 --> 54:25.142
Yeah, fat chance. After what happened last night?
I mean, my mum is just completely freaked out.

54:25.142 --> 54:25.960
- It's not prim.

54:26.000 --> 54:29.801
- Alright, you go do your good girl thing
