call her, get her back here.

01:08:11.960 --> 01:08:12.130
- Ok.

01:08:14.600 --> 01:08:16.413
<i>- Come on, Jill!</i>
<i>- Leave a message.</i>

01:08:16.790 --> 01:08:18.880
- She's not picking up. What's going on?

01:08:18.920 --> 01:08:22.670
- The killer called, he's coming after
me. But he wants my family first.

01:08:22.670 --> 01:08:24.380
- Oh God, Jill...
- Let's get the cops.

01:08:25.140 --> 01:08:26.215
- The cops aren't there.
- What?

01:08:26.466 --> 01:08:28.800
They were there when I first came
in, but they re not there now.

01:08:28.840 --> 01:08:29.697
- Let's get to Kirby's.

01:08:34.044 --> 01:08:35.024
Out the front.

01:08:43.647 --> 01:08:46.013
Press up on the bottom. Can you?

01:08:52.447 --> 01:08:53.281
Let's get out of here.

01:08:54.751 --> 01:08:57.316
Kate, come on! Kate!

01:09:09.045 --> 01:09:13.602
- Tell Jill I am so sorry...
- No, no, no, no, shhhh...

01:09:25.008 --> 01:09:25.852
Kate...

01:09:42.575 --> 01:09:43.880
- Hicks. What are you doing?

01:09:43.920 --> 01:09:46.546
- I just saw somebody coming
around the side of the house.

01:09:46.651 --> 01:09:48.559
Where are Hoss and Perkins? I
couldn't get em on the radio.

01:09:50.240 --> 01:09:55.483
- Whose blood is that?
- Is... Is Kate's, we were just attacked. She's dead.

01:09:55.588 --> 01:09:57.745
- Where is she?
- The front door.

01:09:58.235 --> 01:09:59.518
- Show me.
- Ok.

01:10:04.429 --> 01:10:05.440
- Stay here.
- Ok.

01:10:11.737 --> 01:10:17.191
This is Deputy Hicks. I've got a homicide at the
Roberts residence. No sign of Perkins or Hoss.

01:10:17.608 --> 01:10:20.151
- Copy that. We'll try to locate em.
- I'm so sorry.

01:10:31.881 --> 01:10:38.377
You're gonna be fine, alright? I swear. No more
on your own. It's you and me, forever.

01:10:40.952 --> 01:10:41.681
Easy.

01:10:43.422 --> 01:10:44.850
- Dewey.
- Yeah?

01:10:47.290 --> 01:10:49.510
Promise me something.
- Anything.

01:10:50.722 --> 01:10:56.122
- Catch that motherfucker.
- Absolutely. I love you.

01:10:56.122 --> 01:10:57.029
I love you.

01:10:59.676 --> 01:11:03.952
- It was chaos. Utter chaos.
- I can't believe that.

01:11:03.952 --> 01:11:08.372
The Sheriff's wife, man. She told us to cancel it and we
didn't and now this? What are we supposed to do?

01:11:08.372 --> 01:11:10.352
Robbie, calm down. It makes sense.

01:11:10.769 --> 01:11:13.450
- This is about the reboots too. They-they-they
one up the original ending.

01:11:13.762 --> 01:11:17.160
- "The Woodsboro murders" ended
at a party, so in the remake...

01:11:17.200 --> 01:11:19.601
- ...The party is the false ending. New rules.

01:11:19.883 --> 01:11:23.886
- Exactly.
- Ok, no offense guys but I'm gonna put in Stab 7.

01:11:23.886 --> 01:11:25.658
- Yes...
- Nobody cancels my film festival.

01:11:25.939 --> 01:11:29.640
Wohaa, I don't wanna watch that.
Not after what happened to Olivia.

01:11:29.680 --> 01:11:31.611
- Oh, come on. It was her favorite.

01:11:31.611 --> 01:11:35.230
Oh, wow Kirby. You have some classics here.
- Yep.

01:11:35.230 --> 01:11:37.080
"Suspiria","Don't look now"...

01:11:37.120 --> 01:11:41.069
- You know it. I can trivia your ass
under the table, cinema boy.

01:11:41.069 --> 01:11:45.312
Oh, yeah? Who played Leatherface first?
- Gunnar Hansen.

01:11:45.312 --> 01:11:48.199
Wow, did you feel that?

01:11:49.732 --> 01:11:54.498
- The charge that moved between us, then?
- Oh, that was me. I have powers.

01:11:54.811 --> 01:11:56.103
So sexy...

01:11:57.177 --> 01:12:00.760
You guys are unbelievable. You re playing fucking
trivia games? The cops are gonna come for

01:12:00.800 --> 01:12:02.400
us, they are gonna shut down my website.

01:12:02.400 --> 01:12:04.756
- We re so dead!
- Yeah. I agree.

01:12:04.756 --> 01:12:06.520
- Jesus Christ, where did you come from?

01:12:06.560 --> 01:12:10.053
- The front door. By the way Kirby, with
everything that's going on right now...

01:12:10.053 --> 01:12:14.223
...you probably shouldn't leave that unlocked.
- Sorry...

01:12:14.922 --> 01:12:20.552
- And... May I ask what the hell are you doing here?
- Why, didn't I find the after-party?

01:12:21.011 --> 01:12:26.891
- No, you found the Anti-party and it's invitation only.
- Yeah, well, I got an invitation. From Jill.

01:12:29.247 --> 01:12:33.115
So, what's the story?
- What?

01:12:33.709 --> 01:12:39.235
- You sent me a text message.After-party at Kirby's
