- They always are.

01:42:27.636 --> 01:42:31.149
- Oh, God...
- Nice one.

01:42:33.140 --> 01:42:39.261
- Hicks, you're alive?
- Wear the vest, save your chest.

01:42:42.253 --> 01:42:47.955
I got two officers down, several injuries and a new suspect.

01:42:50.084 --> 01:42:52.408
We need a doctor, Goddammit!

01:42:53.315 --> 01:42:55.609
I dunno about you, but I feel a whole lot better.

01:42:59.539 --> 01:43:05.836
We're live at Woodsboro Community Hospital, awaiting
a first public statement from Jill Roberts, survivor.

01:43:05.836 --> 01:43:10.362
...a survivor of what is now being called
"the Woodsboro Massacre reboot"...

01:43:10.362 --> 01:43:13.949
...Jill Roberts is her name. A name
the whole world will now know...

01:43:13.949 --> 01:43:19.130
...who single-handedly put a stop to this
21st century Woodsboro killing spree...

01:43:19.130 --> 01:43:25.400
...Jill Roberts of Woodsboro, a girl who's
lifted all our spirits tonight. An American

01:43:25.440 --> 01:43:27.648
hero, right out of the movies.

